messages.message:
Hi team,

Cass has brought up an issue where table cells in human review have their values disappear right after entry, as seen in the video I'm attaching here. It doesn't look like anything is amiss in the HAR files (though I know we're only getting the outbound 'set records' API PUT call in them), and wanted to ask how else I might investigate a root cause for these values disappearing.
CC: @Travis @Udit is this a frontend request queueing issue?
